{"tid":236722,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日本比香港有教養？","createTime":"2017-05-10T02:34:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T04:12:18.000Z","uid":31940,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d4665905cdd5332cb2804af4160f4bddfe8e617","tid":236722,"uid":31940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:34:04.000Z","msg":"話說尋日一個人自閉食lunch, 係food court搵到個位。<br />\n對面兩個食完走左，之後見到有幾個中一左右講日文既細路搵位。<br />\n搵到我果張，佢地三四個人，但淨係坐低一個係我斜對面，其他淨係企係到等又唔坐。<br />\n我起身走時有一個向我鞠躬講arigadoe, 果下真係令我有啲驚訝。<br />\n反觀香港好多都問左冇人之後圍住你坐低迫你走咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n撇開日本人自帶種族優越感同啲奸狡行為，<br />\n佢地係基本禮儀家教同國民教育的確冇得頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be847ab52916a74d746fd4daffc7cf06f8e94c7","tid":236722,"uid":74778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:42:23.000Z","msg":"地球村，加 劣幣驅良幣理論，<br />\n好既野會慢慢消失<br />\n日本對比香港，好似香港對比大陸咁。"},{"pid":"7e300587ebe2d2d5f04f644d3b2336e0c4ba38bc","tid":236722,"uid":31940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T03:27:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf5ead6c7e442a2c2015ac56298ad4abae7ba06","tid":236722,"uid":39608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:12:18.000Z","msg":"我個人覺得企係到俾我仲大壓迫感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}